{"tid":802332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個唔交暑期功課嘅大話","createTime":"2018-09-01T11:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T12:07:39.000Z","uid":19638,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6c195d57664ef83dd3c3d4ca720c80f4313a5c","tid":802332,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"我最記得有一次小學<br />\n暑假玩得太癲唔記得左做功課<br />\n同miss講話屋企隻狗食左份功課<br />\n咁啱開學前一晚老母煮羊腩煲<br />\n就順便影相print出嚟做證據<br />\n話為左懲罰隻狗就煮佢嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個miss : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06309957c2024f5bc0c78046249dbd29e6984f7","tid":802332,"uid":199725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"冇做"},{"pid":"ed5fafbec9281dbba91454f3fd460e2f446d6f87","tid":802332,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c06309957c2024f5bc0c78046249dbd29e6984f7","tid":802332,"uid":199725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"冇做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"個老師唔鬧唔罰咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab380fb9df289169a855f9a304bc07e87d73a77","tid":802332,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb2165773ed536d13f1491941e552843ec55b99","tid":802332,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ad68551fcee74532eac3a7b9994357517b86a6","tid":802332,"uid":200258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0